title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-2.10 - Wet storage
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-2.10 - Wet storage

State Regulations

Packaged food is not to be stored in contact with water or undrained ice. Wrapped sandwiches are not to be stored in direct contact with ice. Notes
